hopobject.body: An envelope champix heure de prise Yes, he does. He knows exactly what the motivation is, knows that baseball is doing its best to rid the sport of a player who chose not to follow the laws of the game and the drug agreement between the players and the owners; doing its best to prosecute those who try to hinder its probe of drug cheats and drug pushers, which it sure charges that Rodriguez did with its Biogenesis investigation.
